# lido-deposits-submission

Review the [Lido documentation](https://docs.lido.fi/deployed-contracts/) to find the node operator registry address for the appropriate network. 


Example:

```
go run . --deposit-data=/path/todeposit_data.json --operator-registry-address=0x9D4AF1Ee19Dad8857db3a45B0374c81c8A1C6320
```

Outputs:

```
Opening deposit data file: /path/todeposit_data.json 
Found 10 key signature pairs in deposit data.
No operator ID provided. Looking up operator ID by name "Prylabs"
Operator ID: 44
Send the following call data to the Lido node operator contract at address 0x9D4AF1Ee19Dad8857db3a45B0374c81c8A1C6320
Calldata = 
```
